TI  - Meta-analysis of field-saturated hydraulic conductivity recovery following wildland fire: Applications for hydrologic model parameterization and resilience assessment
PY  - 2017
T2  - Hydrological Processes
VL  - 31
IS  - 21
SP  - 3682
