TI  - Assessing the potential effect of different land cover management practices on sediment yield from an abandoned farmland catchment in the Spanish Pyrenees
PY  - 2011
T2  - Journal of Soils and Sediments
VL  - 11
IS  - 8
SP  - 1440
EP  - 1455
